  “Venice e5 Siong-jin5” Khai3-iau3 
  Venice e5 seng-li2 lang5 Antonio khoaN3-kiN3 i e5 chhin-iu2 Bassanio ai3 beh khi3 Belmont kiu5-hun ti7 chit8 e5 chin ho2-giah8, siong7-chhiaN2 chin sui2 e5 sio2-chia2 mia5-kio3 Portia, u7 khiam3-eng7 chiN5-hang7, sim-koaN chin kan-khou2, put-chi2 tong5-cheng5 i, chong2-si7 tu2-tng7 i pun2-sin bo5 hian7-kim, sou2-i2 u7 khi3 ka7 i peng5-si5 put-chi2 iam3-ouN3, hit e5 pang3 tang7-lai7 e5 Iu5-thai3 lang5, kio3-choe3 Shylock, beh ka7 i chioh 3000 Ducat lai5 hou7 i. Chong2-si7 chit e5 Shylock siong5-siong5 bat hou7 chiah e5 Christian bu2-jiok8, chau-that i, ma7 i pang3 tang7-lai7; sou2-i2 sim-toe2 chin bo5 hoaN-hi2, chhe7 ki-hoe7 beh ka7 in po3 oan-siu5. Chin tu2-ho2, tu2-tng7 Antonio lai5 beh ka7 i chioh 3000 ducat, i sui5-si5 tah-eng3 i, kong2 i bo5 beh ka7 i theh8 tang7 e5 li7-sek, kan-ta tioh8 lip8 khoe3-iok sia2 beng5, na7-si7 ke3 ki5-han7 e5 si5, tioh8 chiong i seng-khu e5 bah chit8 kun lai5 choe3 kho-liau7. 
  Au7-lai5 Bassanio kiu5-hun ti7 Portia e5 sio2-chia2 e5 su7, tit-tioh8 seng5-kong, soa3 seng5-hun, ia7 siang7 hit-si5 i e5 peng5-iu2 Gratiano ia7 kap Nerissa kiat-hun. Tai7-ke teh hoaN-hi2 e5 tiong-kan, hut-jian5 siu-tioh8 Antonio e5 phoe kong2: ─ I e5 siong-chun5 u7 kong3-phoa3, u7 tu2-tioh8 pho3-san2 e5 un7-beng7, siong7-chhiaN2 tui3 Shylock chioh hit tiau5 che3-bu7 ia7 boan2-ki5, boe7-tit-thang heng5, sou2-i2 Shylock u7 sou3-siong7 ti7 hoat-teng5, iau3-kiu5 beh chhu2 i seng-khu chit8-kun e5 bah. Bassanio ui7-tioh8 beh kiu3 i e5 chhin-iu2 Antonio, chiu7 koaN2-kin2 tng2-khi3 Venice. I e5 bou2 Portia sim-lai7 ia7 u7 phah-sng3 e5 sou2-chai7, chiu7 ka2-chong lam5-chu2, chheng choe3 Padua e5 Bellario phok-su7 e5 tai7-li2; toa3 Nerissa ke2-choe3 i e5 su-ki3, ia7 koaN2-kin2 khi2-sin khi3 Venice e5 hoat-teng5, Portia eng7 sim2-mih8 ki5-ti3 lai5 kiu3 i e5 tiong7-hu e5 chhin-iu2 Antonio. Ti7 chit-tiuN5 chin chhut-mia5 e5 tiuN5-bin7, chiu7-si7 Venice e5 hoat-teng5 teh-beh lai5 kai2-koat. Chit chhut iu5-goan5 si7 Eng-kok e5 bun5-ho5 Shakespeare chok--e5. 
  Venice e5 Hoat-teng5 
  Kong-chiok, Kui3-chok8, Antonio, Bassanio, Gratiano, Salerio i2-kip8 ki5-thaN chhut-tiuN5. 
  Kong-chiok: Antonio u7 chhut-teng5 a2 bo5? 
  Antonio: U7, Kok-ha7, ti7-chia. 
  Kong-chiok: Goa2 thoe3 li2 chin kho2-lin5, in-ui7 li2 ui7-tioh8 beh tap-pian7 chit e5 boe7-oe7 lin5-bin2 lang5, bo5 chit8-sut-a2 chu5-pi sim, hui-to7 e5 ok-han3, bu5-cheng5 e5 goan5-ko3, chiah tioh8 lai5 hoat-teng5. 
  Antonio: ThiaN-kiN3 kong2 Kok-ha7 ui7-tioh8 chit chan5 su7 put-chi2 chhut-lat8 lai5 khou2-khng3 goan5-ko3, chong2-si7 i chit8-sut-a2 beh thiaN, siong7-chhiaN2 put-lun7 ju5-ho5 hoat-lut8-siong7 e5 chhiu2-toaN7, boe7-tit-thang kiu3 goa2 thoat-chhut i e5 tok8-sim e5 hoan7-ui5, sou2-i2 goa2 i2-keng chap8-hun jim2-nai7 kiong5-chi3 lai5 ti2-khong3 i e5 loan7-pou7, eng7 leng2-cheng7 e5 sim-koaN, toa7 e5 kak-gou7 beh jim2-siu7 i e5 chan5-gek8 e5 hui-ui5. 
  Kong-chiok: Lin2 chit8 e5 khi3 tiau3 hit e5 Iu5-thai3 lang5 jip8-teng5. 
  Salerio: I ti7 mng5-goa7 teh tan2. Ah! Kok-ha7, i chit-chun7 jip8-teng5 lah! (Shylock jip8-tiuN5) 
  Kong-chiok: Siam2-khui, hou7 i thang khia7 ti7 pun2-koaN e5 bin7-cheng5. (Tui3 Shylock) Shylock ah, lang5-lang5 to teh siuN7, goa2 ia7 si7 an2-ni, ti7 chit e5 su7-be2, kiat-kiok8 li2 teh-beh kai2-oaN7 li2 kau3 taN sou2 khng3 phaiN2 e5 sou2 siuN7, pi2 hit-si5 li2 sou2 chheng2-kiu5, khoaN3 liau2 chin ki5-koai3, chin chan5-jim2 e5 su7; li2 teh-beh eng7 koh-khah ki5-koai3 e5 khoan2-sit lai5 piau2-si7 li2 e5 chu5-pi kap lin5-bin2; ia7 li2 sou2 iau3-kiu5 e5 kho-liau7, chiu7-si7 chit8 e5 sin3-sit8 e5 seng-li2 lang5 e5 bah chit8-kun, put-tan3 li2 bo5 beh kiong5 chheng2, kau3 be2 soa3 siu7 jin5-cheng5 chu5-ai3 e5 kam2-tong7, lai5 bian2-tu5 hit e5 kho-liau7, m7-na7 an2-ni, goan5-kim li2 ia7 beh ka7 i kiam2-chio2 toa7-pou7-hun7. Kun7-lai5 pi7-ko3 e5 sin-chiuN7, liok8-siok8 lui2-chip8 e5 sun2-sit, li2 beh eng7 lin5-bin2 e5 bak8-chiu lai5 khoaN3; sit8-chai7 kan-ta an2-ni e5 sit-pai7 i2-keng kau3-giah8 ap-to2 chit e5 sin-siong, lian5 hit khoan2 sim-koaN bu5-cheng5 chhin-chhiuN7 thih-chioh8 e5 lang5, a2-si7 bo5 koan3-si3 ti7 chu5-pi chhin-chhiat e5 su7, hiah e5 goan2-kiong5 e5 Thou2-ni2-ki5 lang5, a2-si7 That8-tan2 lang5, na7 khoaN3-kiN3 chit khoan2 chong7-thai3, un2-tang3 beh siN-khi2 chit8 phiN3 tong5-cheng5 e5 sim-liam7! Pun2-koaN i2-kip8 it-tong5 teh ki5-thai7 li2 teh-beh eng7 chin un-sun5 e5 oe7 lai5 tap-pian7 siaN2 khoan2? Iu5-thai3 lang5 ah! 
  Shylock: Lun7 goa2 e5 chun5 i3, i2-keng siong7-sin liau2! Goa2 u7 ki2 seng3-jit8 lai5 chiu3-choa7, tiaN7-tioh8 iau3-kiu5 chiau3 cheng3-su-bin7 sou2 ki3-beng5, chiu7-si7 lang5-bah chit8-kun. Ka2-su2 Kok-ha7 na7-si7 ku7-choat8 bo5 beh hou7 goa2 e5 si5, chiu7 Kok-ha7 li2 tui3 goa7-kok lang5 sou2 hou7 in e5 tek8-hu2, i2-kip8 li2 sou2 koan2-hat Venice hu2 chu7-iu5 e5 teng2-bin7, un2-tang3 oe7 hoat-seng toa7 e5 gui5-hiam2. Kiam2-chhai2 Kok-ha7 teh-beh mng7, siaN2-su7 goa2 m7-tih8 saN-chheng “ducat”, hoan2-tng2 beh tih8 chit8-kun bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 bah ia7 kaN2! Chong2-si7 che goa2 khiok m7-bian2 in3-tap, na7 ai3 chai, thang kong2 si7 goa2 e5 sim-koaN chit8-si5 sou2 ai3, an2-ni kaN2 u7 liau2-kai2!? Ka2-su2 goa2 e5 chhu3 u7 hou7 chit8 chiah niau2-chhu2 khou2-chhou2, ui7-tioh8 beh tok8-sat hit chiah niau2-chhu2, goa2 hoaN-hi2 lai5 siau-hui3 saN-chheng ducat e5 si5, siaN2 khoan2?! Li2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 lai5 tap-pian7?! U7 lang5 bo5 ai3 khoaN3 khui-chhui3 e5 ti; ia7 u7 lang5 khoaN3-tioh8 niau oe7 khi2-siau2, koh-chai3 u7 lang5 thiaN-tioh8 hong-tek8 e5 siaN ia7 oe7 hoat-kong5, che kiu3-keng3 si7 lang5 e5 seng3-phiah, ia7 chiau3 hit e5 lang5 e5 seng3-phiah e5 chi2-hui khoaN3 i e5 sou2 ai3 si7 sim2-mih8, i e5 khi3-hun chiu7 hiong3 hit peng5, na7 bo5 ai3--e5, chiu7 oat8 hong-hiong3 ti7 pat8-ui7. Sou2-i2 tui3 ti7 Kok-ha7 goa2 ia7 beh an2-ni lai5 tap-pian7. SiaN2-su7 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 khui-chhui3 e5 ti, chiu7 tong3-boe7-tiau5? SiaN2-su7, put-tan3 si7 bo5 hai7, hoan2-tng2 iu2-ek e5 niau ia7 bo5 ai3 khoaN3? Ia7 thiaN-tioh8 iuN5-mng5 choe3 e5 hong-tek8 chaiN2-iuN7 chiu7 tong3-boe7-tiau5? Chong2 kong2, ka-ki7 e5 kam2-chhiok siu7 chou2-gai7 e5 si5, un2-tang3 oe7 ham7-loh8 ti7 oh-tit siam2-pi7, oe7 hai7-tioh8 pat8 e5 kam2-chhiok e5 thi2-jiok8, an2-ni lun7 hit tiam2, boe7-tit-thang lai5 khak-teng7 hit e5 li2-iu5; siang7 chit8-iuN7, goa2 ia7 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 li2-iu5 thang kong2, siong7-chhiaN2 ia7 bo5 siuN7 beh tap-pian7! Goa2 tui3 pi7-ko3 the5-chhut iau3-chheng2 chit8 khoan2 sih8-pun2 e5 sou3-siong7, kiu3-keng3 si7 goa2 tui3 ti7 pi7-ko3 u7 khng3 siok-oan3 kap liam5-ok ti7-teh, chhut chit hang7 i2-goa7, si7 bo5 u7 sim2-mih8 pat8 khoan2 e5 li2-iu5 ti7-teh! An2-ni kaN2 u7 liau2-kai2 chiah tioh8!? 
  Bassanio: Li2 chit khoan2 bu5-cheng5 e5 lang5! An2-ni kiam2 oe7 choe3 li2 tap-pian7 li2 chan5-gek8 e5 hiong5-pian7 e5 pian7-kai2 mah !? 
  Shylock: Goa2 bo5 hit khoan2 gi7-bu7 tioh8 tap-pian7 hou7 li2 hoaN-hi2! 
  Bassanio: Lang5 kiam2 long2-chong2 hai7-si2 in sou2 bo5-ai3--e5 mah!? 
  Shylock: Lang5 tak8 e5 kiam2 u7 oan3-hun7 in sou2 bo5-ai3--e5 mah!? 
  Bassanio: Put-khoai3 e5 kam2-cheng5 kap oan3-hun7 e5 kam2-cheng5 bo5 tek-khak si7 siang7 chit8-iuN7! 
  Shylock: EhN! Li2 ai3 hou7 tok8-choa5 ka7 li2 ka7 nng7-pian3 mah? 
  Antonio: Bassanio, li2 tioh8 siuN7, li2 si7 teh kap bu5-cheng5, khek-pok8 e5 Iu5-thai3 lang5 gi7-lun7! Li2 na7 oe7 soat-hok8 i e5 sim-koaN, li2 ia7 kho2-i2 khia7 hai2-piN beng7-leng7 toa7-iuN5 e5 toa7-eng2 piN3 choe3 soe3 e5 eng2; ia7 thang kap chhai5-long5 ke3-kau3, khoaN3 i siaN2-su7 ka7-si2 iuN5-bu2, ia7 pang3 ku3-chai7 iuN5-kiaN2 hau2 beh chhe7 i e5 lau7-bu2! Iah8 ma7 oe7 thang kim3-chi2 soaN-teng2 be2-liu e5 chheng5-peh-chhiu7, hou7 toa7-hong chhe lai5 chhut toa7 e5 siaN. Ki5-thaN bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 ui5-lan5 e5 su7 ia7 oe7 chiaN5! Sit8-chai7 ti7 chit e5 se3-kan bo5 chit8 hang7 pi2 beh iong5-ho5 Iu5-thai3 lang5 e5 sim-koaN khah ui5-lan5 e5 su7! Sou2-i2 bo5 pit-iau3 koh kong2-khi2, boh8-tit koh gi7-lun7 khah ho2, leng7-kho2 chhu2 kan2-tan e5 chhiu2-siok8 koaN2-kin2 lai5 siu7 chhai5-phoaN3, thang hou7 Iu5-thai3 lang5 boan2-chiok i e5 sou2 ai3! 
  Bassanio: Beh heng5 li2 e5 3000 ducat, ti7 chia u7 toa3 6000 lai5, beh siu bo5? 
  Shylock: Ka2-su2 li2 e5 6000 ducat e5 tiong-kan, mui2 chit8 e5 ducat phoa3 choe3 6 phiN3, ia7 kok phiN3 chiaN5-choe3 chit8 ducat goa2 ia7 bo5 siuN7 beh siu. Goa2 iau3-kiu5 chiau3 cheng3-su bin7 lai5 li2-heng5.
  Kong-chiok: Li2 bo5 kiaN5 chu5-pi, hit-tiap8 li2 na7 khiam3-eng7 chu5-pi e5 si5 beh chaiN2-iuN7? 
  Shylock: Lang5 na7 bo5 oai-ko chhih8-chhoah8, u7 sim2-mih8 thang kiaN chhai5-phoaN3 e5 su7? Goa2 sou2 iau3-kiu5 chit8-kun e5 lang5 bah si7 chin ko-ke3 lai5 boe2--e5, si7 goa2 e5 sou2-iu2-but8, sou2-i2 bo5 tit-tioh8 boe7 boan2-i3. Li2 na7-si7 kong2 m7 hou7 goa2 e5 si5, chiu7 li2 e5 kok-ka sou2 teng7 e5 hoat-lut8, si7 kap bo5 siang7 chit8-iuN7! Ia7 Venice e5 cheng3-leng7 si7 kui khang-khang! 
  Kong-chiok: Goa2 eng7 Kok-chu2 e5 koan5-lek8, theng3 ho2 beng7-leng7 pi3-teng5, chong2-si7 u7 chhiaN2 chit8-ui7 phok-hak8 e5 phok-su7, kio3-choe3 Bellario, lai5 kai2-koat chit chan5 su7, i kin-a2-jit8 oe7 lai5. 
  Salerio: Kok-ha7, tu2-chiah tui3 Padua u7 su2-chia2 toa3 phok-su7 e5 su-sin3 lai5 ti7 mng5-goa7 teh theng3-hau7. 
  Kong-chiok: Na7-si7 an2-ni, su-sin3 theh8--lai5, ia7 chhiaN2 su2-chia2 jip8--lai5. (Nerissa, chng-choe3 hoat-lut8-ka e5 su-ki3 jip8--lai5). 
  Kong-chiok: HouN7! Li2 si7 tui3 Padua, Bellario phok-su7 hia lai5 mah? 
  Nerissa: Si7, Kok-ha7, Bellario phok-su7 beh ka7 li2 chheng2-an, (chin3-cheng5 chiong su-sin3 hian3 hou7 Kong-chiok). 
  Bassanio: SiaN2-su7 li2 hiah chhut-lat8 teh boa5-to? 
  Shylock: Beh koah bah koh8! Khia7 ti7 hia hit e5 pho3-san2-chia2 e5 heng-kham2-bah! (pi2 ka-ki7 e5 heng-kham2). 
  Gratiano: Ngi7-sim e5 Iu5-thai3 lang5, li2 eng7 oe5-toe2 boa5-to, m7-tat8-tioh8 eng7 li2 sim-toe2 hit te3 teng7-chioh8 lai5 boa5, kam2 m7-si7 khah oe7 lai7 mah? Chong2-si7 bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 khoan2 lai7 e5 to-khi3, a2-si7 cham7 thau5-khak e5 pou2-thau5, na7 eng7 li2 toe2 chioh8 lai5 boa5, sit8-chai7 thang kiaN lang5! Iu5-thai3 lang5 ah, bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 ki5-goan7, kiam2 ko2-jian5 boe7 koan3-thiat li2 e5 sim-koaN mah? 
  Shylock: Boe7, na7-si7 siong-eng3 li2 e5 ti3-hui7 e5 ki5-to2, si7 bo5 hoat-tou7 lah! 
  Kong-chiok: Chiau3 Bellario chit tiuN phoe, i u7 chhui-ku2 chit8-ui7 lian5-siau3 e5 hoat-hak8 phok-su7 lai5 lan2 e5 hoat-teng5. I ti7 to2-ui7? 
  Nerissa: I teh theng3-hau7 Kok-ha7 un2-chun2 i jip8 teng5. 
  Kong-chiok: Chin hoaN-hi2 hoan-geng5--i, lin2 kui2-na7 lang5, chiau3 le2-sou3 khi3 an3-nai7 i lai5 chit e5 sou2-chai7! (Portia jip8-tiuN5, chheng7 hoat-hak8 phok-su7 e5 hok8-chong). Oh, Sian-siN chiu7-si7 tui3 Bellario lo2-ong hia lai5--e5 mah? 
  Portia: ChiaN3-si7, Kok-ha7! 
  Kong-chiok: Chin lo5-hoan5 li2 lai5, chhiaN2 che7! Hian7 si5 tong hoat-teng5 teh sim2-gi7 e5 an3-kiaN7, koan-he7 Goan5, Pi7-ko3 liong2-peng5 sou2 tin5-sut8 e5 su7, m7-chai li2 i2-keng thiaN-tioh8 mah? 
  Portia: Goa2 i2-keng chai chin siong5-se3! Pi7-ko3 e5 seng-li2 lang5 ti7 to2-ui7? Goan5-ko3 e5 Iu5-thai3 lang5 ti7 to2-ui7? 
  Kong-chiok: Antonio kap Shylock, nng7 lang5 long2 chhut-lai5 thau5-cheng5. 
  Portia: Li2 chiu7-si7 Shylock? 
  Shylock: Si7, Shylock si7 goa2 e5 mia5! 
  Portia: Chit pang li2 sou2 the5-chhut chit e5 sou3-siong7, thang kong2 si7 ki5-koai3 e5 lah! Chong2-si7 chhiu2-siok8-siong7 bo5 chit8-sut-a2 m7 tu2-ho2 e5 sou2-chai7, sou2-i2 tui3 Venice e5 hoat-lut8 piau2-bin7-siong7 lai5 khoaN3, si7 bo5 thang hiam5! (tui3 Antonio). Li2 e5 siN-si2 tioh8 ai3 it-jim7 ti7 goan5-ko3 chiah oe7 eng7--tit. 
  Antonio: Si7, i an2-ni chu2-tiuN! 
  Portia: Tui3 ti7 cheng3-su, u7 iN7-gi7 a2-bo5? 
  Antonio: Bo5! 
  Portia: Na7-si7 an2-ni, Iu5-thai3 lang5 tioh8 ai3 si-sia3 chu5-pi chiah oe7 eng7--tit. 
  Shylock: Si7 hou7 sim2-mih8 kiong5-pek--tioh8, goa2 tioh8 si-sia3 chu5-pi? ChhiaN2 kong2 beng5. 
  Portia: Sou2-ui5 chheng choe3 chu5-pi-chia2, m7-si7 kiong5-heng5 e5 seng3-chit e5 mih8. Tioh8 chhin-chhiuN7 bi5-soe3 e5 hou7, tui3 thiN loh8-lai5 toe7-bin7, lai5 lun7-tek8 thou2-toe7! Chu5-pi u7 nng7-teng5 e5 hok-khi3, chiu7-si7 hou7--lang5-e5, kap nia2-siu7--e5, Chu5-pi na7-si7 tui3 ui2-tai7 e5 lang5 lai5 chhut, chiu7 oe7 hian2-chhut choe3 ui2-tai7 e5 hau7-ko2; koh-chai3 chu5-pi si7 pi2 ong5-koan koh-khah oe7 hou7 kun-ong5 tit-tioh8 eng5-kng. Kun-ong5 sou2 gia5 e5 chau3-pan2 (笏=hut) si7 piau2-si7 siok8-kai3 e5 koan5-lek8, si7 kiaN-hiaN5, ui-giam5 e5 goa7-bin7-tek e5 ki3-ho7, chiu7-si7 piau2-si7 kun-ong5 si7 kho2-ui3 e5 i3-gi7. Na7-si7 chu5-pi si7 pi2 kun-ong5 sou2 gia5 e5 chau3-pan2 koh-khah u7 lat8, si7 ku-chiam3 ti7 khah koan5 e5 ui7-ti3, chiu7-si7 ku-chiam3 ti7 kun-ong5 e5 sim-cho7 si7 siok8 ti7 Thian-te3 seng3-chit e5 chit8-pou7-hun7, ji5-chhiaN2 chu5-pi lai5 tiau5-ho5 kong-to7 e5 si5, hit-si5 chiah oe7 sit8-hian7 siok8-kai3 e5 koan5-lek8 kap Thian-kai3 e5 koan5-lek8 hap8-it. Sou2-i2 Iu5-thai3 lang5 ah, sui-bong2 li2 e5 pian7-lun7 si7 siok8 ti7 kong-to7, iau2-ku2 li2 chim-chiok lai5 siuN7 chit8 chan5 su7! Chiu7-si7 ti7 kong-to7 e5 lou7-siong7, bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5 si7 boe7-tit-thang siok8-choe7, lan2 tui3 Thian-te3 ai3 tit-tioh8 I sia3-choe7, tioh8 ai3 kiu5 I e5 chu5-pi. Chiu7-si7 iu5-goan5 ka3-si7 lan2 tioh8 oh8 I si-sia3 chu5-pi. Goa2 ui7-tioh8 beh iong5-ho5 li2 sou2 pian7-lun7 e5 kong-to7, sou2-i2 chiah an2-ni lai5 pian7-lun7. Tan7-si7 li2 na7 kiong5-tiau7 li2 e5 chu2-tiuN e5 si5, Venice giam5-cheng3 e5 hoat-teng5, tek-khak tioh8 ai3 tui3 hit e5 siong-jin5 lai5 soan-ko3 chiah oe7 eng7--tit. 
